devops - is not a applicaiton rather a modern idea that solve the issues bet 
         developers and operations and to improve collaboration 
       - to make it possible devops idea use a tons of tools like:
            

Continous Development  -- tools use (git,svn)
Continous Integration --- tool used (Jenkins)
Continous Deployment ---- Docker for Virtualization and Containerization  Puppet and Ansible for Configuration Management
Continous Testing    ---- tool used Selenium 
Continous Monitoring ---- tool used Nagios